name: electron-triage-for-github
description: Desktop app for dividing GitHub issues and pull-requests into go or no-go quickly.

packageJSON.name: triage-for-github
packageJSON.description: Desktop app for dividing GitHub issues and pull-requests into go or no-go quickly.

scripts.build:dev: npm run clean && npm run resource && webpack --config webpack/webpack.application.config.dev.js
scripts.build:dist: npm run clean && npm run resource && webpack --config webpack/webpack.application.config.production.js
scripts.build:local: npm run clean && npm run resource && webpack --config webpack/webpack.application.config.js
scripts.electron: npm run build:dev && cd dist && electron . 2>&1 | silence-chromium ../debug.log && cd ..
scripts.eslint: npm run eslint:es5 && npm run eslint:es6
scripts.lint: npm run eclint && npm run eslint
scripts.resource: cpy package.json dist && npm run resource:main
scripts.resource:main: cpy lib/main.js dist && cd dist && npm install electron-debug electron-template-menu && cd ..
scripts.verify: npm run lint && npm run test && npm run build:local && npm run build:dev && npm run build:dist
